&lt;p&gt;Maybe we should backport &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17428&quot; title=&quot;reduce default value for lru_max_age to 300s&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17428&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17428&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to b2_15 fix this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="477567" author="yujian" created="Fri, 7 Nov 2025 16:25:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+2 on b2_15 branch:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/d95bf5a0-9d71-4a8f-9a60-49c56939966e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/d95bf5a0-9d71-4a8f-9a60-49c56939966e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/298b325b-b8a1-412c-8979-23b9185d4589&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/298b325b-b8a1-412c-8979-23b9185d4589&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="428230" author="adilger" created="Mon, 16 Sep 2024 23:58:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The recent increase of test_10a failures on master (71x since 2024-09-02) may be related to the landing of patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/53682&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/53682&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17428&quot; title=&quot;reduce default value for lru_max_age to 300s&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17428&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17428&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ldlm: reduce default lru_max_age&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; on 2024-08-30.  It may be necessary to temporarily increase &lt;tt&gt;lru_max_age&lt;/tt&gt; for this test to pass consistently.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One issue is that if test_10a is modified the &lt;tt&gt;subtest-change&lt;/tt&gt; session will run it in a loop, and the client eviction message will no longer appear on the console.  That needs to be fixed in conjunction with this change, or in a preparatory patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
